											</div>
					<h2 class="blv-hdng">We <span>Believe</span>
</h2>
				<p>Resurgence Hall K-8 Charter School believes that every student is entitled to a rigorous, college preparatory education regardless of their economic circumstances, zip code, race, or home language. We educate our students to meet the following measures of success: </p>
				<p class="para"><i class="fa fa-star" style="font-size:16px;color:#FA9731"></i> 100% of students will enroll in college preparatory courses in high school and be on track for success in college.</p> 
