												<div class="feature-desc">
							<h4>Design Thinking</h4>
							<p>Resurgence Hall is deeply committed to answering one central question: “How can we create a high quality 21st century learning experience for all students?”</p>						</div>
					</div>
										<div class="feature-item col-md-4 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.2s">
